-- Munich Re Concludes Investment Deal for Wind Energy in Germany
-- B y   M i k e   G a v i n
-- 2010-12-23T11:35:33Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-12-23/munich-re-concludes-investment-deal-for-wind-energy-in-germany.html
Munich Re said it has concluded an
investment deal in Germany through its MEAG asset manager
whereby it will acquire 40 wind turbines with a total output of
73 megawatts. The investment is in the “low three-digit million
range,” the company said in an e-mailed statement today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Mike Gavin at 
 mgavin2@bloomberg.net  